{
  "stem": "942.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--what grandfather said, you know, this was the last word, you know?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was quite a discussion.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he left, you know?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we just--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember his name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember he had a green uniform on that he always used to wear, you know, like britches, you know, with high boots.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he had this hunting hat, you know, with-- not feathers, but like a bristle, you know, from-- And he-- well, I guess he must have-- wherever he was the night before, you know, in a pub or somewhere, I guess, he heard this from the gendarmes, when they were drinking there.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Somebody must have slipped a word, you know, that this is what's going to happen the next day.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he left.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The gates were locked.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I guess we went back to bed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There wasn't much sleep after that, because, at the crack of dawn-- it was probably 6:30, I guess, in the morning-- an unusual thing happened.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, we had a town crier in town, because that's the way the news were reported, you know, any laws from the mayor, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was this little fellow who went to different spots in town.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he had a drum.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he played his drum for a few minutes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that meant that everybody has to come and listen what he has to say.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then he took out this roll of paper.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he had a very loud voice.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he felt he was a very important person.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And this happened right in front of our house.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And, you know, we belonged to a different municipality.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we never had this town drummer in front of our house.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And this happened that morning.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
